column52:
To overturn the decision in the uk due to perjury. I will keep this sort but we have all seen the proof that Amber heard faked her evidence in support of her abuse accusations against Johnny Depp. 

Johnny lost the uk trial due to all this evidence which has since been proven to be fake and Miss Amber Heard should face PERJURY charges! 

The fact she also told the uk courts that she had DONATED all her settlement to charity, which , as also been proven to be a LIE! 

Both her ‘ evidence ‘ and testimony, were the reason Johnny lost the uk trial and now.. it has been proven that Amber had committed perjury in the uk as well as in the current trial in Virginia. 

Johnny deserves a retrial and the world deserves his truth!
